<div id="intro">
	Submitting a mod to the {{ REPONAME }} hosted Mod Repository for Summoner : Modloader for Scrolls
	will add your mod to the repository review queue. When the people running this repository have 
	finished reviewing your mod, it will be added to this repository, making it available to every
	player using this repository to download mods for Summoner. Please don't submit mods more than
	once - when it's submitted, people running this repository have received it and will begin reviewing
	it shortly. When your mod is accepted into this repository, you will receive information on how to
	submit updates for your mod. All fields are required!
</div>
<div class="submit">
	<div class="title">
		<h3>Fill out the fields below: <h3>
	</div>
	<div class="submit-form">
		<form method="POST" action="/submit">
			<div>
				<label for="mod-name">Mod Name (no spaces):</label>
				<input type="text" id="mod-name" name="mod-name" placeholder="MyAwesomeMod" />
			</div>
			<div>
				<label for="mod-author">Mod Author:</label>
				<input type="text" id="mod-author" name="mod-author" placeholder="John Doe" />
			</div>
			<div>
				<label for="mod-author-email">Mod Author Email (for communication about new API updates, authentication for submitting mod updates):</label>
				<input type="text" id="mod-author-email" name="mod-author-email" placeholder="example@example.com" />
			</div>
			<div>
				<label for="mod-token">Mod Token (like a password for submitting new updates):</label>
				<input type="text" id="mod-token" name="mod-token" placeholder="mypassword" />
			</div>
			<div>
				<label for="mod-desc-short">Short Mod Description (less than 20 characters!):</label>
				<input type="text" id="mod-desc-short" name="mod-desc-short" placeholder="Scrolls is awesome" />
			</div>
			<div>
				<label for="mod-desc-long">Long Mod Description (includes your mod's functionality, short guide on how to use):</label>
				<textarea id="mod-desc-long" name="mod-desc-long"></textarea>
			</div>
			<div>
				<label for="mod-version">Mod Version Code:</label>
				<input type="text" id="mod-version" name="mod-version" placeholder="0.8" />
			</div>
			<div>
				<label for="mod-repo">Opensource link (link to your repository):</label>
				<input type="text" id="mod-repo" name="mod-repo" placeholder="http://github.com/myawesomemod" />
			</div>
			<div>
				<input type="submit" value="Submit"/>
			</div>
		</form>
	</div>
</div>